The <code><strong>PaymentRequestUpdateEvent</strong></code> interface is used for events sent to a <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest" title="The Payment Request API's PaymentRequest interface the primary access point into the API, and lets web content and apps accept payments from the end user on behalf of the operator of the site or the publisher of the app."><code>PaymentRequest</code></a> instance when changes are made to shipping-related information for a pending <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest" title="The Payment Request API's PaymentRequest interface the primary access point into the API, and lets web content and apps accept payments from the end user on behalf of the operator of the site or the publisher of the app."><code>PaymentRequest</code></a>. Those events are: